I am a PhD student, to clarify for the

1407
01:20:43.192 --> 01:20:47.142
audience. But yeah, I'm very excited to present my work to you, "The

1408
01:20:47.312 --> 01:20:51.112
Impact of Obesity-Induced Changes in Adipose Tissue on Ovarian

1409
01:20:51.172 --> 01:20:52.112
Cancer Progression."

1410
01:20:53.552 --> 01:20:57.452
So ovarian cancer is the most lethal gynecologic malignancy and can be

1411
01:20:57.512 --> 01:21:01.412
categorized into four different stages, where stages one and two is

1412
01:21:01.452 --> 01:21:04.052
where the cancer is confined within the pelvic region.

1413
01:21:04.672 --> 01:21:08.592
And then in stages three and four, the cancer has now spread to

1414
01:21:08.652 --> 01:21:12.592
the omentum, and the omentum is an abdominal fatty tissue sheet that

1415
01:21:12.652 --> 01:21:14.392
covers the peritoneal cavity.

1416
01:21:15.462 --> 01:21:19.292
And unfortunately, at stages three and four, this is where ovarian

1417
01:21:19.332 --> 01:21:22.612
cancer is most frequently caught due to its

1418
01:21:22.622 --> 01:21:26.112
nonspecific symptoms and lack of accurate predictive screening

1419
01:21:26.172 --> 01:21:29.552
tests. So, this makes understanding the

1420
01:21:29.592 --> 01:21:33.032
biology of metastatic colonization to the omentum

1421
01:21:33.772 --> 01:21:35.192
increasingly important.

1422
01:21:36.972 --> 01:21:40.212
When ovarian cancer metastasizes to the omentum, the

1423
01:21:42.192 --> 01:21:46.152
ovarian cancer cells establish a complex tumor microenvironment

1424
01:21:46.232 --> 01:21:49.812
enriched of the cancer cells, pre-adipocytes, adipocytes,

1425
01:21:50.192 --> 01:21:54.172
immune cells, fibroblasts that are secreting its own extracellular matrix

1426
01:21:54.252 --> 01:21:56.532
composed of collagen or fibronectin.

1427
01:21:57.182 --> 01:22:00.452
And there is cell-to-cell communication in the forms of IGF-1,

1428
01:22:00.972 --> 01:22:04.212
IL-6, or TNF alpha as examples. And

1429
01:22:04.612 --> 01:22:08.392
pre-adipocytes are precursors to fat cells, and they make up

1430
01:22:08.432 --> 01:22:12.292
15% to 50% of the stromal cell compartment and are

1431
01:22:12.392 --> 01:22:15.972
an important component of visceral fat.

1432
01:22:16.592 --> 01:22:20.572
And unlike lipid-rich adipocytes, their morphology is

1433
01:22:20.612 --> 01:22:24.242
fibroblast-like, and their secretome is enriched in proinflammatory and

1434
01:22:24.292 --> 01:22:25.632
tumor-supporting factors.

1435
01:22:26.892 --> 01:22:30.392
So a previous graduate student wanted to understand the role of these

1436
01:22:30.412 --> 01:22:33.112
pre-adipocytes in ovarian cancer tumor formation.

1437
01:22:33.152 --> 01:22:37.072
And so she did a limiting dilution injection model

1438
01:22:37.132 --> 01:22:41.032
where she injected 40 cancer cells to one pre-adipocyte, an equal

1439
01:22:41.112 --> 01:22:44.072
ratio of one to one, and then a one to 40 ratio.

1440
01:22:44.542 --> 01:22:45.602
And the

1441
01:22:47.752 --> 01:22:51.632
injections of cancer cells alone were not able to form tumors,

1442
01:22:51.732 --> 01:22:55.612
but with the presence of pre-adipocytes, this significantly enhanced

1443
01:22:55.672 --> 01:22:57.132
tumor growth. And

1444
01:22:58.072 --> 01:23:01.972
this one to 40 ratio is mimicking isolation stress, which

1445
01:23:02.052 --> 01:23:05.752
is a condition characteristic of metastasizing cells

1446
01:23:06.152 --> 01:23:09.452
that are colonizing the omentum where there is an abundance of pre-adipocytes.

1447
01:23:10.312 --> 01:23:14.141
And we further validated with injections of mature adipocytes

1448
01:23:14.172 --> 01:23:17.862
that both pre-adipocytes and mature adipocytes are generating

1449
01:23:17.932 --> 01:23:20.832
tumors similarly, as well as tumor growth.

1450
01:23:21.452 --> 01:23:24.792
And the cells were then subjected to

1451
01:23:24.812 --> 01:23:28.152
co-cultures between pre-adipocytes and adipocytes,

1452
01:23:28.612 --> 01:23:29.852
and there were significant

1453
01:23:30.752 --> 01:23:34.392
hits for cellular response to stress and extracellular matrix

1454
01:23:34.612 --> 01:23:38.032
organization, as well as regulation of IGF

1455
01:23:38.092 --> 01:23:42.012
transport. And I want to emphasize that this RNA

1456
01:23:42.052 --> 01:23:44.891
was taken from the cancer cells in co-culture.

1457
01:23:46.292 --> 01:23:49.932
And specifically here, these pre-adipocytes enrich

1458
01:23:49.942 --> 01:23:50.352
this

1459
01:23:51.492 --> 01:23:55.092
phenotype implicating insulin-like growth factor signaling

1460
01:23:55.112 --> 01:23:56.652
important for these cancer cells.

1461
01:23:57.332 --> 01:24:01.292
And IGF has vital effects on proliferation and survival,

1462
01:24:01.332 --> 01:24:03.682
and it was indeed increased in co-culture

1463
01:24:04.612 --> 01:24:06.582
with pre-adipocytes. And

1464
01:24:07.532 --> 01:24:11.152
IGF stimulation on cancer cells increased ECM

1465
01:24:11.532 --> 01:24:13.972
remodeling genes like collagen and fibronectin.

1466
01:24:14.862 --> 01:24:18.392
And in my preliminary experiments, I'm finding that

1467
01:24:18.472 --> 01:24:21.872
IGF is working in both nutrient-full and nutrient-depleted

1468
01:24:21.912 --> 01:24:25.532
conditions, activating phosphorylated AKT as well

1469
01:24:25.592 --> 01:24:29.332
as phosphorylated p65, which is associated with the

1470
01:24:29.372 --> 01:24:31.872
classical NF Kappa B pathway.

1471
01:24:34.072 --> 01:24:35.492
And obesity

1472
01:24:36.632 --> 01:24:40.232
increases the risk for several cancers, including ovarian, and its

1473
01:24:40.252 --> 01:24:43.692
dysfunctional adipose tissue creates a special and

1474
01:24:43.772 --> 01:24:47.552
permissive niche for ovarian cancer to spread and thrive.

1475
01:24:48.212 --> 01:24:52.152
And in an obesity mouse model, these researchers found that

1476
01:24:52.192 --> 01:24:55.852
there was increased metastasis to the omentum as well as to the

1477
01:24:55.892 --> 01:24:59.632
mesentery, and these are adipose-rich sites.

1478
01:25:00.252 --> 01:25:03.242
And in a different study, these

1479
01:25:03.272 --> 01:25:07.172
omental adipose tissue were taken from obese and

1480
01:25:07.212 --> 01:25:11.092
morbidly obese patients, and there was increased IGF expression as

1481
01:25:11.132 --> 01:25:14.032
