1482
01:25:14.092 --> 01:25:17.852
So all of these potential links led us to want to understand this

1483
01:25:17.912 --> 01:25:21.482
obesity-mediated IGF

1484
01:25:21.592 --> 01:25:24.232
signaling in ovarian cancer metastasis.

1485
01:25:24.272 --> 01:25:27.312
So I have hypothesized that obesity increases

1486
01:25:27.332 --> 01:25:31.212
pre-adipocyte-mediated activation of IGF-1 signaling

1487
01:25:31.272 --> 01:25:31.932
to enhance

1488
01:25:32.772 --> 01:25:36.664
ovarian cancer growth and metastatic ability.So to

1489
01:25:36.674 --> 01:25:40.414
test my hypothesis, I obtained normal BMI preadipocytes

1490
01:25:40.444 --> 01:25:44.364
from female donors or a female donor, and high

1491
01:25:44.444 --> 01:25:46.564
BMI preadipocytes from a different female donor.

1492
01:25:47.184 --> 01:25:51.144
And I did either a co-culture or a co-injection model

1493
01:25:51.304 --> 01:25:54.804
with GFP-labeled cancer cells. And

1494
